Class SnappingNodeMap

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jts.geomgraph.NodeMap
      com.vividsolutions.jts.geomgraph.SnappingNodeMap

public class SnappingNodeMap
extends com.vividsolutions.jts.geomgraph.NodeMap

Repository of nodes of a PlanarGraph that applies a snap tolerance. If we ask for a node, and it founds a node in the tolerance distance it returns the found node.

Author:
azabala
